Juliet Prowse https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Juliet_Prowse 0 Juliet Anne Prowse (September 25, 1936 – September 14, 1996) was a dancer, whose four-decade career included stage, television and film. She was raised in South Africa, where her family emigrated after World War II.
